GeometryTwo
A game made in 48 hours for Ludum Dare 34, Theme: "Growing, Two buttons control"
by RandomTowerOfGames

http://randomtower.blogspot.it/

## Introduction

This simple game was made in 48 hours for Ludum Dare 34, for more info about Ludum Dare, go to http://ludumdare.com/compo/

## Controls

Just your mouse

Left Click: attack enemies

Right Click: reduce your size

Try to keep a balance between size (and firepower) and your life!

## How to compile

Using git clone this repository and clone [MarteEngine maven branch](https://github.com/Gornova/MarteEngine/tree/maven).
Be sure to set lwjgl native for lwjgl (in Eclipse under build path ->  libraries -> native library

